gazeparser (0.11.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bug in calcurating threshold for Microsaccade detection is fixed.
  * Bug in getCameraImageSize() is fixed.
  * "config" option is added to Dummy backend of GazeParser.TrackingTools.

gazeparser (0.11.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Python3 is supported.
  * PsychoPyComponent supports PsychoPy 1.90.0 or later.
  * PsychoPyComponent no longer supports PsychoPy older than 1.84.0.
  * VisionEgg backend in TrackingTools is no longer supporeted.
  * EyelinkToGazeParser() and TobiiToGazeParser() is no longer supported.

 -- Hiroyuki Sogo <hsogo@ehime-u.ac.jp>  Fri, 22 Aug 2018 18:00:00 +0900

gazeparser (0.10.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Manual calibration mode is added.
  * Camera image can be saved.

 -- Hiroyuki Sogo <hsogo@ehime-u.ac.jp>  Fri, 30 Sep 2016 18:00:00 +0900

gazeparser (0.9.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * setup_for_psychopy.py script is added to help installing GazeParser to Standalone PsychoPy.
  * Camera image can be saved by pressing "I" key during preview.
  * fix error in getEyePosition() and getEyePositionList() in dummy mode.

 -- Hiroyuki Sogo <hsogo@ehime-u.ac.jp>  Thu, 08 Oct 2015 18:00:00 +0900

gazeparser (0.8.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * getCameraImageSize(), fitImageBuffer() and setCurrentScreenParamsToConfig() are added to TrackingTools.
  * GazeParserGetPos component is added.
  * A new option "Fit Preview Buffer" is added to GazeParserInit component.
  * TRACKER_ORIGIN, VIEWING_DISTANCE, DOTS_PER_CENTIMETER_H and DOTS_PER_CENTIMETER_V are supported by "Use Monitor Info" option of GazeParserInit component.
  * GazeParserRec component sends "sync_rec" message to PsychoPy's log file.
  * GazeParserMessage component outputs event log.
  * "set every repeat" option is added to "Message (Start)" and "Message (End)" of GazeParserRec component.
  * Bugs in "Mode" option of GazeParserInit component is fixed.
  * A prototype version of wxPython based data viewer is added.

 -- Hiroyuki Sogo <hsogo@ehime-u.ac.jp>  Wed, 2 Jun 2015 18:00:00 +0900

gazeparser (0.8.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * A new option is added to GazeParserInit to toggle sending PsychcoPy's monitor settings to SimpleGazeTracker.
  * Better synchronization between PsychoPy Builder experiment and SimpleGazeTracker.
  * Log messages by PsychoPy Components are improved.
  * Default parameters of PsychoPy Components are modified.
  * Several bugs in PsychoPy Components are fixed.
  * Several bugs in TrackingTools are fixed.

 -- Hiroyuki Sogo <hsogo@ehime-u.ac.jp>  Wed, 25 Mar 2015 18:00:00 +0900

gazeparser (0.8.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * add checkVersion option to GazeParser.Utility.load.
  * GazeParser.Converte.TrackerToGazeParser supports calibration precision/accuracy data of SimpleGazeTracker 0.8.0.
  * Raw calibration/validation data can be saved to SimpleGazeTracker data file (GazeParser.TrackingTools).
  * Custom components for PsychoPy Builder are created.
  * fix error in combining data files (Viewer.py).

 -- Hiroyuki Sogo <hsogo@ehime-u.ac.jp>  Thu, 12 Mar 2015 19:48:31 +0900

gazeparser (0.7.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * remove units='pix' from ControllerPsychoPyBackend.
  * support Pillow.
  * name of camera capture file includes timestamp.
  * Several improvement in Data Viewer.

