gazeparser (0.6.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * 'recordingDate' is added. (GazeParser.Core)
  * 'RESAMPLING' is added (GazeParser.Configuration, GazeParser.Converter)
  * 'compareVersion', 'checkAttributes' and 'rebuildData' are added. (GazeParser.Utility)
  * Several improvement and bugfix in Data Viewer.

