gazeparser (0.6.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Calibration results is simplified. (GazeParser.TrackingTools)
  * Validation can be started only afer calibration has been performed. (GazeParser.TrackingTools)
  * Camera-specific data is supported. (GazeParser.Core, GazeParser.Converter)

